### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Marquer une notification comme lue (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications-mark-notification-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notification_id": "notification-uuid-here"
}

### Test 2 - Marquer plusieurs notifications comme lues
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications-mark-notification-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notification_ids": ["notification-uuid-1", "notification-uuid-2"]
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: notification_id et notification_ids manquants
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications-mark-notification-read
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

